creator: Julia Qian
descriptionHtml:
★★Cameroceras was born★★

Play as real Cameroceras and survive in the wildness as long as you can. Journey to a hidden, untouched Jurassic island and kill the most ferocious animals in history.

FEATURES:

REALISTIC SIMULATOR
Maintain your health and energy by eating dinos and drinking water, explore massive world, fight other dinosaurs to become more powerful

REAL WEATHER SYSTEM
Realistic day-night cycle. With correct sun and moon positions with full location support with latitude and longitude. Seasons will auto changed. Also supports temperature simulation, based on season, time of day and current weather. It includes 11 weather types including: " Clear Sky", "Cloudy", "Raining", "Storm", "Snow" and "Foggy" weather.

EXPERIENCE AMAZING GRAPHICS
Dynamic shadows, hi-res textures and realistic Jurassic models all combine to make this one of the most beautiful dinosaur simulator games on your mobile device!

A AVARIETY OF SKILLS
With the upgrade, you can unlock different skills and experience wonderful magic effects.

Other enemy dinosaurs include: Velociraptor, Troodon, Iguanodon, Compsognathus, Pteranodon, Styracosaurus, Parasaurolophus, Protoceratops, Pachycephalosaurus, Gallimimus, Dilophosaurus, Ankylosaurus, Argentinosaurus, Carnotaurus, Brachios, Steaurus, Pteratosaurus, Raptor

ADDITIONAL FEATURES
-RPG-style gameplay: level up, evolve, complete quest
-Customize your Cameroceras
-Realistic jungle environments
-Realistic dinosaur sound effects
-Fast faced, action packed 3D Dinosaur Simulator
-Quest system
-Open World Style game
-Awesome 3D graphics
